Topics of discussion:
*410-120-0045 - Applications for Medical Assistance at Provider locations. Rule is being revised in order to remove references to CoverOregon; 
*410-120-1320 - Clarification to drug copay table; 
*943-120-0350 - Senate Bill 204 required OHA develop uniform payment methods. Stakeholder groups were formed and rules were promulgated for Medical Assistance and PEBB/OEBB contracts in 2011/2012. However, an overarching rule was not promulgated for OHA. This is to correct that oversight.

Discuss language changes to consolidate CCO and MCO rule requirements into one rule and Incorporate revised language for:
*School-Based Health Services (SBHS); 
*Type A and B Hospitals, to better reflect current practices; 
*Pharmacy PA requirements

Topics of discussion:
-Review needed language changes in order to consolidate the CCO and MCO rule requirements into one rule; 
-Incorporate revised language regarding School-Based Health Services (SBHS);
-Update rule language for Type A and B Hospitals to make the language more reflect current practices. 
-Pharmacy PA requirements
